        <h1>Fitness Plan (26-40 Overweight)</h1>
        
        <h2>Diet Plan</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Breakfast:</strong> Green smoothie (spinach, banana, almond milk, protein powder).</li>
            <li><strong>Lunch:</strong> Grilled fish with quinoa and roasted vegetables.</li>
            <li><strong>Snacks:</strong> Low-fat yogurt with flaxseeds.</li>
            <li><strong>Dinner:</strong> Stir-fried chicken with brown rice and steamed greens.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Gym Routine</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Low-impact cardio (brisk walking, cycling) for 30-40 minutes daily.</li>
            <li>Strength training with light weights 2-3 times a week.</li>
            <li>Core and mobility exercises for flexibility.</li>
        </ul>
